{
  "stem": "22869.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was one time in Auschwitz, and then in Birkenau, where the people who worked there would, in fact, take all the suitcases that came in from newcomers, unpack them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were boys and girls in that camp and would do the sorting of the stuff under the SS supervision.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a camp, that in a certain extent, was, of course, much better than the other camps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "First of all, you had food galore, because in all the packages, there was all this food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a person can only eat so much, so everybody was sharing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was really asked by a guy who was also from Czechoslovakia-- I forgot its name.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Rosenwasser, ?] or whatever what his name was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You come to me and you will see that under my guidance-- he was-- he was the blockalteste, or the kapo, whatever, in this detail.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That you will have all the food you will need, and you'll see, you will have it good.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so forth and so forth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I came along with him to that camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was just a different section from Birkenau, because it was divided in-- I don't remember exactly today-- G-D-C-F and so forth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were the neighboring place to the crematoria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In other words, after us was already the Sonderkommando 1, where the crematorium and the gassing was going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, you could see in the night from where we were, from the chimney smoke and fire going out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you knew, and you could smell the burning of the bodies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But this-- when we came to this place, of course, everybody who came to this place-- I don't remember how many of us were there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
